name: TURBO CHARGERS!
description:
GET READY TO GO TURBO!!

Turbo Chargers the lost Ante-Comp classic has finally been uncovered and carefully reconstructed by the Team at Mycho Digital. 

Join Rose and Phazer as they battle against alienated vechicles hellbent on stripping the earth of its precious Cannisters of Distilled Crystal Fuelarium and only these Turbo Charged Teen Racers can stop them. 

Battle across TWO unique levels and gain the BIGGEST score you can as you GO TURBO!!!

Find more info athttp://mycho.co.uk
